Dialogs.Dialog: ▲主人公＊▲. I have something to ask you.
▲新主人公▲. Can I call you like this？
I'm glad. It's a little embarrassing but I just wanted to try it▼
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
▲新主人公▲. How about this one？
I think you'd better stop that.
Isn't it already good the way it is？
If I call you like this from now on, what would you say？
Hehe. I like it when you listen to what I say like this.
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
▲新主人公▲. How about this one？
Isn't it already good the way it is？
Geez. I was being daring and all.
▲新主人公▲. Are you happy when I call you like this？
Really？ Then I'll call you this way.
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
▲新主人公▲. How about this one？
Okay, so I'll call you this way from now on.
Isn't it already good the way it is？
How about I called you like this？ You like it？
It's so embarrassing but I think you might like it.
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
▲主人公＊▲. If you like this name, I'm fine with it.
Yeah, no good. You scared me.
(Tsk. So this is no good, huh...？)
Ah... Really？ Fine. Just forget it.
Hey, how do you like it？
Right. I knew you'd like this.
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
(Tsk. So this is no good, huh...？)
Hey, you're that happy. So cute▼
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
Well, I have no choice, huh？
I see. So you like it like that...
(Tsk. So this is no good, huh...？)
(The way I call ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ now... Shall I try changing it...？)
I should keep it the same
Okay. If you want to call me like that, it's fine.
You don't have to be shy！
That's not the case. ...Just don't call me like that.
(The way I call ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ now... Shall I try changing it...？)
I should keep it the same
Hey, you don't have to be that happy.
I don't think that's a good idea.
Haha, you like it？ It's good, right？
(The way I call ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ now... Shall I try changing it...？)
I should keep it the same
That's okay. Can you call me again？
Hehe. You look so happy. You're cute▼
You shouldn't call me like that, okay？
Well, if you really want to...
Yes, yes. I really want to.
But, no. I really don't like this name.
